Activity Summary: Type of compound activity based on both the aromatase antagonist mode readout and the cell viability counter screen.
Antagonist Activity: Type of compound activity in the aromatase antagonist mode screen.
Antagonist Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of aromatase.
Viability Activity: Type of compound activity in the cell viability counter screen.
Viability Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of cell viability.
